curl \
  -X POST \
  -H "content-type: application/json" \
  localhost:3001/editor/letter_of_recommendation/evaluate \
  --data-binary @- <<EOF
{
  "text": "Dear [Admission Committee],I am pleased to write this letter of recommendation for [Student’s Name] who is applying for admission to your esteemed [Program Name] at [University Name]. I have had the privilege of teaching [Student’s Name] for the past [Number] years in my [Subject] class at [School/College Name]. During this time, I will be consistently impressed with [his/her/their] academic performance, intellectual curiosity, and dedication to learning. [Student’s Name] stands out for [his/her/their] acceptional analytical abilities and critical thinking skills. [He/She/They] has demonstrated a remarkable ability to grasp complex concepts and apply them effectively in various assignments and projects. [His/Her/Their] contributions to class discussions have been insightful and thought-provoking, often leading to a deeper understanding of the subject matter for [his/her/their] peers. Beyond academics, [Student’s Name] is also actively involved in [mention any extracurricular activities, leadership roles, community service, etc.]. [He/She/They] has shown a strong comitment to [specific activity or cause], which speaks volumes about [his/her/their] character and dedication to making a positive impact on society. In terms of personal qualities, [Student’s Name] is a highly motivated and disciplined individual. [He/She/They] approaches challenges with a positive attitude and a willingness to learn from mistakes. [His/Her/Their] perseverance and resilience are truly commendable. I am confident that [Student’s Name] will be an asset to your university and will continue to excel in [his/her/their] academic and personal pursuits. [He/She/They] has my highest recommendation, and I strongly urge you to consider [him/her/their] application favorably. Please feel free to contact me if you need any further information."
}
EOF